flowchart TD
    RCTX[Pemancar RC\ninput pilot] -->|2.4 GHz RF| RCRX[Penerima RC\nPWM / SBUS]
    RCRX -->|kanal hardware| FC

    JOY[Joystick USB\nopsional] -->|RC_CHANNELS_OVERRIDE\nmelalui MAVLink| FC

    CAM[Kamera\nOpenCV] -->|frame| SK[Seeker\ndeteksi / lacak\nCamShift · MeanShift · MIL · CSRT\nDaSiamRPN · Nano · ViT · Kalman]
    SK -->|cx cy| EXY[error_xy\nerrorx errory ∈ -1..1]

    EXY -->|error mentah| PRED[Prediktor Latensi\n+ PN lead]
    PRED -->|error terprediksi| SM[State Machine Mode\nRule 1/2/3 · deteksi tepi ch6]

    FC[Flight Controller\npymavlink] -->|telemetri RC_CHANNELS| SM
    FC -->|HEARTBEAT  mode terbang| SM
    FC -->|ATTITUDE roll pitch yaw| TEL[Polling Telemetri]
    FC -->|GLOBAL_POSITION_INT lat lon alt| TEL
    FC -->|VFR_HUD airspeed throttle| TEL

    TEL --> HUD[HudDisplay\ntape yaw · tangga pitch · roll]
    TEL --> CSV[Logger CSV\nsaat --debug]

    SM -->|MAV_CMD_DO_SET_MODE\nTRACKING / AUTO / STABILIZE| FC
    SM -->|error tracking x y\nsaat tracking + terkunci| FC
    SM --> HUD
    SM --> CSV
